CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 27, 1954, pg. 13 reads: "The Glamorous Cotillion - Scenes from the third annual debutante Cotillion given by Pittsburgh AKAs include..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of thirteen men wearing tuxedos with tails and light colored gloves, standing in Syria Mosque for the Alpha Kappa Alpha's 1954 Cotillion
